Full biography of famous Iranian singer and artist Samyar Ghodrati

((Samyar Ghodrati the singer of the famous song Man Barat Bass Mizanam))

Samyar Ghodrati an Iranian singer, composer, songwriter, and arranger who in early 2004 with the songs Metropolis and khab Sefid.

Entered the Iranian music market...

He is also known as the King of Beis or the Sultan of Beis.
And with the extremely beautiful and dreamy bass song ((Man barat bass mizanam )) it became popular and became world famous.
Until today, he is the owner of more than 68 musical works in the big market of Iranian music
He also owns 5 official albums
